{"tid":1589310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"非法禁錮 False Imprisonment","createTime":"2019-09-23T08:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:34:16.000Z","uid":279102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1d9101a6c4a891cc60068b0b64883f6be0b1f0","tid":1589310,"uid":279102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"警務處處長：<br />\n<br />\n現在我向你舉報，你和你下屬在 24/8/2019 及在 15/9/2019 濫用警權，分別拘捕劉穎匡和許智峰，涉嫌觸犯非法禁錮罪。<br />\n<br />\n因轉承責任法理依據，你需舉你下屬共同承擔刑事罪行。<br />\n<br />\n請告知我相關報案編號，以便我在網頁 <a href=\"http://www.hkscandal.com/policecrime1908_09falseimprisonment.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkscandal.com%2Fpolicecrime1908_09falseimprisonment.html&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=88029214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkscandal.com/policecrime1908_09falseimprisonment.html</a> 作跟進用途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝振中總警司：<br />\n<br />\n你在記者招待會上曾說：「謝振中認為真相對警隊清白好重要，可能是警員犯錯，亦可能只是誣衊，故投訴的人士應站出來提供證據」。我現在就在你面前舉報你的上司和同事涉嫌觸犯非法禁錮罪。  這條罪行是 strict liability offence，控方的舉証責任非常簡單，而被告需要證明自己沒有犯法，與謀殺罪的舉証剛好相反。 另外，strict liability offence 不需要考慮意圖成份 (mens rea)。<br />\n<br />\n這張電郵會被上載到 <a href=\"http://www.hkscandal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkscandal.com&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0fab2c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkscandal.com</a> 網站之等候回覆（不回覆＝點認）的分類內。極度歡迎你回覆，而你的回覆也會出現在同一網頁內，讓公眾人士自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何超光<br />\n香港一位最卑微的小市民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190824/bkn-20190824233018672-0824_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190824%2Fbkn-20190824233018672-0824_00822_001.html&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=2d6292bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190824/bkn-20190824233018672-0824_00822_001.html</a>  警方以涉嫌非法集結拘捕劉頴匡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/nono/POERN19010049C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fnono%2FPOERN19010049C.pdf&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=ebfbce25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/nono/POERN19010049C.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190921/mobile/odn-20190921-0921_00176_011.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190921%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190921-0921_00176_011.html&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=7989b5a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190921/mobile/odn-20190921-0921_00176_011.html</a>   劉穎匡被非法禁錮  24/8/2019   POE RN 19010049<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23639/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E5%8F%8D%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-23653/%E3%80%90%E9%80%86%E6%AC%8A%E5%8F%8D%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E3%80%91%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E5%90%8C%E6%99%9A%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%913%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E7%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E7%B4%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23639%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-23653%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2586%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%25913%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25AE%2597%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B4%25A2&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=